    • Constructor Detail

      • TableAnimation

        public TableAnimation(ITable table,
                      double[] columnLayout,
                      double[] rowLayout)
        Initializes a new instance of the TableAnimation class for the given table, the column widths, and row heights.

        Note that only the sizes of leaf stripes, i.e. those without child stripes, are considered. The sizes of a stripe with children is implicitly determined by its contents.

        Parameters:
        table - The table to animate.
        columnLayout - The sizes of the leaf columns, in natural order.
        rowLayout - The sizes of the leaf rows, in natural order.
